                    href="#"
                    >Sign in
                  </a>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="mt-3">
                <p class="mx-auto text-sm leading-tight text-center text-white">
                  Not a have a password? <a
                    class="ml-3 text-vanta-300 hover:text-white"
                    href="/signup">Sign up now</a
